{"tid":1095023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"出街食得健康係咪奢侈品","createTime":"2019-04-06T17:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T17:41:15.000Z","uid":69273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84d5935871a21a9e4d58936bc79f55e3fbe6e0c6","tid":1095023,"uid":69273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:28:44.000Z","msg":"屋企冇飯食 收工又晏 長期三餐出去食<br />\n本身個人飲食習慣都唔算好 <br />\n<br />\n想問大家有冇啲平民 健康的餐廳推薦<br />\n又唔想俾一大嚿錢食啲懶高級豐富營養的貴價健康餐<br />\n<br />\n都係想簡簡單單食餐營養均衡 價錢合理的飯<br />\n日常多數係紅色同藍色線 求推薦"},{"pid":"03d0d7050b20967873401720b9e2c469188f320d","tid":1095023,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:30:39.000Z","msg":"出街食，食菜貴過食肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb7f3c2fa3c33c69d749213f2a033efbf5656df","tid":1095023,"uid":2002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"屋企煮 蒸下菜咪得"},{"pid":"b6269cf62ca32246d9c14a1a20186dfbf9690113","tid":1095023,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"連登不二之選<br />\n大快活紅米雞胸飯"},{"pid":"5842b5cdb1d934afbc9e3c0a22ed9e4df122c186","tid":1095023,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb7f3c2fa3c33c69d749213f2a033efbf5656df","tid":1095023,"uid":2002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"屋企煮 蒸下菜咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:37:20.000Z","msg":"收工收得晏<br />\n無心機洗食材，煮，洗碗<br />\n有時間既幸福人係唔會明"},{"pid":"b0acf3682e53d4f8689e2eabbec65e63e12b4799","tid":1095023,"uid":119050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"雞胸紅米飯走汁 大快活"},{"pid":"e1b3f8316e6b136937ae31e2879cb2948974ff03","tid":1095023,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:41:15.000Z","msg":"閒閒地食個飯都要5-60以上，覺得健康既又好似唔係咁抵，炒個小菜加個白飯好似好少少<br />\n<br />\n同埋都要買返多d生果食"}]}